item.description:
The 5th annual Not About the Building spelling be is once again upon us.  Watch 36 people attempt to riddle out how to spell strange words by asking for definitions and etymology for your viewing pleasure.

Perhaps you think you can spell well and want to sign up?  Newcomers members have participated in the past 2 competitions, but not yet won a prize.

Free to Watch, bar on site, $8 to sign up to participate, Signups at 8:30, spelling starts at 9pm.

Wagering on spelling contestants is also allowed, and all proceed go to fund Not About the Buildings activities and event planning.
item.how_to_find_us: I'll try to be obvious, with a sign
item.name: The Annual Not About the Building Spelling Bee
